data.description: BACK ON THE MARKET! USDA 0% Down Financing Eligible! Discover the epitome of comfort and serenity with this home in Franklin Township, NJ. This 4-bedroom, 2-full bath residence offers a perfect blend of modern convenience and natural tranquility.  Nestled on a generous 3.58-acre lot, the home offers a serene retreat from the world, with a large fenced-in yard surrounded by wooded views, providing the utmost privacy. The upper level unfolds into a thoughtfully designed living room, dining room, and kitchen, adorned with granite countertops and an island perfect for culinary creations and gatherings. The upper-level offers a full bath and three bedrooms, with one featuring brand-new carpeting.  The home's layout also includes a lower-level family room (or bonus room), bedroom, closet space and full bathroom allowing for privacy and easy access to the backyard through a walkout. Crown molding and recessed lighting add a touch of sophistication throughout the home. Rest easy knowing that major updates have been taken care of, including a 2018 septic system, 2017 HVAC installation, and a new 2022 condenser,  new ejector pump in 2022 and  newer well pump ensure peace of mind. **Back on the market!**
